fridges.name: Loisaida CommUnity Fridge
fridges.notes:
Open 24/7

Accepts: cooked food (labeled and dated), raw/fresh foods (fruits, vegetables, dairy, meat), non-perishables (jarred or canned foods, rice, beans, pasta, cereal), non-food items (toothpaste, soap, other personal care items, we cannot accept clothing), pet food (wet and dry, please label). 

Requirements: Unopened, fresh, ideally healthy food; cooked food must be labeled with ingredients.
